OL,4,Cindefinite leave to remain to be
OL,5,Cannounced
OL,7,FMigrants who want to remain in the UK
OL,8,Fwill have to learn English to a high
OL,9,Fstandard, have a clean criminal record
OL,10,Fand volunteer in their community, the
OL,11,Fhome secretary is set to announce.
OL,13,FShabana Mahmood will outline a series
OL,14,Fof conditions for those seeking
OL,15,Findefinite leave to remain status at
OL,16,Fthe Labour Party Conference on Monday.
OL,18,FAsylum seekers will also need to be
OL,19,Fworking, paying national insurance and
OL,20,Fnot be claiming benefits under the
OL,21,Fproposed changes.
