OL,7,FLabour said there is a "dividing line"
OL,8,Fbetween the government's proposals and
OL,9,FReform UK's pledge to scrap settled
OL,10,Fstatus for all non-EU migrants.
OL,12,FA consultation on the changes will be
OL,13,Flaunched later this year.
OL,15,FIn its White Paper published in May,
OL,16,Fthe government also pledged to
OL,17,Fincrease the amount of time migrants
OL,18,Fhave to wait before they can apply for
OL,19,Findefinite leave to remain in the UK
OL,20,Fto ten years.
