OL,7,FMahmood will argue that her toughness
OL,8,Fon secure borders, fair migration and
OL,9,Fsafe streets are essential components
OL,10,Fof an "open, generous, tolerant"
OL,11,Fcountry.
OL,13,FShe will also warn party members that
OL,14,F"you won't always like what I do".
OL,16,FMahmood will speak about her parents'
OL,17,Fexperience of arriving in the UK,
OL,18,Farguing the acceptance of migrants
OL,19,Fdepends on their contribution to local
OL,20,Fcommunities.
